### Subject API Endpoints

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api/Subject

### Add New Subject
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "subjectName": "Mathematics",
  "subjectCode": "MATH101",
  "classId": 1,
  "teacherId": 1,
  "credits": 4,
  "type": "core",
  "description": "Introduction to Mathematics covering algebra, geometry, and calculus basics."
}

### Get All Subjects
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Subject By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE